Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.15,0:00:34.88,Campus Common,星南,0,0,0,,
Comment: 0,0:00:32.15,0:00:34.88,Campus Common,星南,0,0,0,,待って、まず写真を撮るわよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.08,0:00:38.62,Campus Common,燕,0,0,0,,
Comment: 0,0:00:35.08,0:00:38.62,Campus Common,燕,0,0,0,,む、SNSにアップするのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.82,0:00:44.16,Campus Common,星南,0,0,0,,
Comment: 0,0:00:38.82,0:00:44.16,Campus Common,星南,0,0,0,,ええ！　最新のトレンドはこのアプリを\n使うらしいわよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.35,0:00:46.60,Campus Common,燕,0,0,0,,
Comment: 0,0:00:44.35,0:00:46.60,Campus Common,燕,0,0,0,,なぜ伝聞調なんだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.80,0:00:52.01,Campus Common,星南,0,0,0,,
Comment: 0,0:00:46.80,0:00:52.01,Campus Common,星南,0,0,0,,仕事で忙しいと、プライベートの写真を\n撮る機会がないのよね……
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.15,0:00:58.94,Campus Common,星南,0,0,0,,
Comment: 0,0:00:54.15,0:00:58.94,Campus Common,星南,0,0,0,,ん～、とっても美味しいわね、燕！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.14,0:01:02.91,Campus Common,燕,0,0,0,,
Comment: 0,0:00:59.14,0:01:02.91,Campus Common,燕,0,0,0,,私はもう限界だ……うっぷ……
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.11,0:01:04.69,Campus Common,星南,0,0,0,,
Comment: 0,0:01:03.11,0:01:04.69,Campus Common,星南,0,0,0,,あら、早いわね。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.90,0:01:08.23,Campus Common,燕,0,0,0,,
Comment: 0,0:01:04.90,0:01:08.23,Campus Common,燕,0,0,0,,甘すぎるものは苦手なようだ……
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.43,0:01:15.16,Campus Common,星南,0,0,0,,
